    <description>
       <![CDATA[
			<h3 class="template-title nudge">Shiraz for Anahita ™</h3>
			
			<p><img src="../templates/shiraz/images/anahita_logo.png" alt="Anahita Social Engine" class="template-thumb" /></p>
			
			<p>
			<b>Shiraz [ʃiːˈrɒːz]</b> Named after the ancient city of poets, mathematicians, flowers, and wine 
			in south of Persia which dates back to 4000 BCE.  
			</p>
			
			<p>
			This template is developed for the Anahita ™ Social Networking Platform and Framework and the Anahita ™  
			Social Apps by <a href="http://www.anahitapolis.com" target="_blank">Anahitapolis.com</a>. 
			It is available to you under the <a href="http://gplv3.fsf.org/" target="_blank">GPL3</a> license.
			<p>
			
			<p>This template provides styling for the following social apps:</p>
			<ol>
				<li>Topics</li>
				<li>Photos</li>
				<li>Groups</li>
				<li>Connect</li>
				<li>Todos</li>
				<li>Pages</li>
			</ol>
			
			<p>The Anahita™ Shiraz template is developed using the Gantry Framework and Twitter Bootstrap 2.0</p>
			]]>			
            </description>
